	title = {Antibiotic resistance and distribution of serotypes of invasive pneumococcal strains isolated from hospitalized adults in Lima, Peru; [Resistencia antibiótica y distribución de serotipos en cepas neumocócicas invasivas en adultos hospitalizados en Lima, Perú]},
